content: Hi all! We are kicking off the main webinar now with a few morning announcements, then Richard Ettema will be presenting an Intro to FHIR session that will last about an hour and be a great place for beginners to start.

Hi everyone! Hope you're off to a good start on your Track Zooms! Join the main webinar now for an Intro to the Logica FHIR Sandbox!
https://global.gotowebinar.com/eojoin/1861438407741376527/3154766448283513867

Hey everybody guess what?!!! Richard Ettema will be presenting FHIR Tools and Touchstone on the Main Webinar at 11:30! Join here: https://global.gotowebinar.com/join/over.tmpl?webinar=7701337188753883917
John Loonsk is on the main webinar sharing his work on eCR Now FHIR App for COVID-19 Electronic Case Reporting. Go watch while you eat your lunch. No lunch ticket required!
